xxl.applications.io
Class RecordManagerTest

java.lang.Object
  xxl.applications.io.RecordManagerTest

public class RecordManagerTest
extends Object

A simple test class for the record manager. That includes the test of the Strategy, the Page and the Block Classes.

insert

public static void insert(Map map,

Performs an insertion, so that numberOfObjects records are inside the RecordManager after the execution. The records are of random size around pageSize/4.
